DESCRIPTION: Set the logs feature on your server.
EXTENDED_LINE_1: **{{prefix}}setlogs setup** ~ Setups the entire serverlog feature on your server.
EXTENDED_LINE_2: **{{prefix}}setlogs roles #channel** ~ Sets a channel to be used for the role-logs in your server.
EXTENDED_LINE_3: **{{prefix}}setlogs member #channel** ~ Sets a channel to be used for the member-logs in your server.
EXTENDED_LINE_4: **{{prefix}}setlogs message #channel** ~ Sets a channel to be used for the message-logs in your server.
EXTENDED_LINE_5: **{{prefix}}setlogs other #channel** ~ Sets a channel to be used for the other-logs in your server.
EXTENDED_LINE_6: **{{prefix}}setlogs channel #channel** ~ Sets a channel to be used for the channel-logs in your server.
EXTENDED_LINE_7: **{{prefix}}setlogs public #channel** ~ Sets a channel to be used for the public-logs in your server.
EXTENDED_LINE_8: **{{prefix}}setlogs voice #channel** ~ Sets a channel to be used for the voice-logs in your server.
EXTENDED_LINE_9: **{{prefix}}setlogs modlogs #channel** ~ Sets a channel to be used for the mod-logs in your server.
SETUP: The server logs channels have been set up and will now log everything for you. The public logs channel is still private and all default logs have been set up to log publically in this channel. Once you feel it is ready, feel free to make this channel readable by everyone to show how active your server is.
REASON: Channel created for setlogs setup usage.
NEED_ROLELOGS_CHANNEL: You did not provide a channel to use for the role-logs.
NEED_MEMBERLOGS_CHANNEL: You did not provide a channel to use for the member-logs.
NEED_MESSAGELOGS_CHANNEL: You did not provide a channel to use for the message-logs.

NEED_CHANNELLOGS_CHANNEL: You did not provide a channel to use for the channel-logs.
NEED_PUBLICLOGS_CHANNEL: You did not provide a channel to use for the public-logs.
NEED_VOICELOGS_CHANNEL: You did not provide a channel to use for the voice-logs.
